aors.module.evt
Interface ModuleEventListener

All Known Implementing Classes:
AORJavaGui, AORJavaWebStartGui
public interface ModuleEventListener

The ModuleEventListener offers an interface for module events listeners. While modules may send events to the simulator, this interface must be implemented by any module event listeners. be used all over the simulator.

Since:
25 April 2010

Method Summary
 void moduleEvent(ModuleEvent moduleEvent)
          Modules may send back events for informing listeners about some states.
 

Method Detail

moduleEvent

void moduleEvent(ModuleEvent moduleEvent)
Modules may send back events for informing listeners about some states. This method is called whenever a such event must be trown.

Parameters:
moduleEvent - the module event about which the listeners are notified.
